<!--
  AEGIS AETHER  -  ON-DEMAND playlist feed  -  EXAMPLE
  ====================================================
  Mode: ON-DEMAND. No shared wall-clock. Each listener starts at item 1 and
  plays in order at their own pace. Same spec shape as the synced station
  (medium=musicL, ordered remoteItems, value routing, curation cut) but with
  NO anchor-time semantics: order is just playlist order.

  Mixed content: podcast segments + Wavlake music tracks in one list. medium
  is still musicL here (a curated list dominated by music); use mixed if the
  blend is heavier on non-music. Each remoteItem carries its own medium.

  Per-segment REMOTE VALUE ROUTING via valueTimeSplit + nested remoteItem:
  remotePercentage to the original creator's feed, residual to the station
  owner as an ADDITIONAL recipient (curation cut). Originals never mutated.

  All GUIDs / URLs FICTIONAL but realistically shaped. Wavlake feed/track
  GUIDs are illustrative, not real Wavlake identifiers.
  (See ../pc20-namespace-capability-map.md.)
-->
